snippet.title: Mortal Kombat 1 – Official Homelander First Look
snippet.description:
Scorched earth. Blood and bone. Homelander is coming to Mortal Kombat 1.

The Boys Season 4 premieres June 13.

Get the Premium Edition and play as Homelander when he arrives: https://www.mortalkombat.com/purchase

It's In Our Blood. Discover a reborn Mortal Kombat Universe created by Fire God Liu Kang. Mortal Kombat 1 ushers in a new era of the iconic franchise with a new fighting system, game modes, and Fatalities!
